section.div: The Bioinformaticians Interactive Lab Notebook (BILN) is a smart, dynamic system for tracking experiments, datasets, and workflows. Designed for bioinformaticians, it ensures reproducibility, structured logging, and AI-readiness. Export logs, collaborate seamlessly, and let BILN become your interactive companion in computational biology.
